snippet.title: Feed and Grow: Fish - Teaser
snippet.description:
Find food, hunt other fish and simply, grow into larger beasts! 

Animal survival game based in the fish world! You start as Bibos or Raptor the fish and straight away you are ready to dive in to the waters of the mesmerizing world of Feed and Grow. 

Beta version with multiplayer out now on Steam :) Let us know what you think http://store.steampowered.com/app/429050

Download or  Play Feed and Grow from our official site 
http://www.feedandgrow.net/
